node.text:
Dinner delivery from Saveur yesterday which I had fun re-plating again. 😄

My family enjoys dining at Saveur and their Duck Confit is our all time favourite. For our home delivery meal, we decided to order something different.
.

We ordered the Traditional French Pot Roasted Chicken 1.3kg that comes with root vegetables, potatoes & Herb Pilar Rice ($35, good for 2-4pax) and Chargrilled Australian Ribeye Steak 200g, served with choice of 
Sauce and Two Sides. ($22).
.

Saveur has recently launched their online food delivery store - shop.saveur.sg offering Islandwide Delivery. With this one-stop-shop, they are offering their Signature dishes & Ice Cream from their 4 Concepts namely Saveur, MediumRare, FrapasBar and Bread & Butterfly.
.
. . [𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐌𝐎𝐓𝐈𝐎𝐍]
Keen to try? In the month of May & June, Baking Taitai’s followers can enjoy10% off all orders on top of ongoing promotions when you use the promo code “TAITAI10OFF” at checkout. (Minimum order is $50, delivery fee $5. Free delivery for orders above $100)
.
.
Thank you Saveur Sg for reaching out to me and arranging a delicious meal for my family! .
.
.
.
.

@darr3n0ng  First time trying their roasted chicken, not bad and rather tender! 😋
@thefatfam_ it’s not bad, above our expectation rather tender! 😋
Yum!! I love their duck confit too! Will try their roasted chicken next 😍
@sherbakes going back for their duck confit when they reopen again!
Wow it looks good!!!! Love their duck confit
@qingxiangsqx yea the chicken is huge and good for the 4 of us!
Wah what a feast! I'm tempted to order the whole chicken, but there's only two of us 😅
@jo.wonder Thanks, that’s why I enjoy replating it so that food looks more appetizing 😄
Wow! Looks really delish 😋The replating definitely makes the food more inviting.. 💗💕👍🏼
@ariane.le going back for their duck confit when they reopen again! 😋
Oh I love their Duck Confit! It's also my favourite!! 😍😍❤️❤️❤️
